high_descs: Turn around, walk down the room and to the diningtable with a knife on your right.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Go to the kitchen corner on your left that begins just on your left, next to the table, stop at the kitchen sink and lean down to reach the lettuce cabinet.
Cut a lettuce inside the cabinet with the knife.
Put the knife in the cabinet.
Pick up a lettuce from the cabinet.
Lean back up at the sink.
Place the lettuce in the sink, rinse it up, then take it out.
Turn around, go straight to the entrance in front of you, continue straight parallel to the bed and, standing in the middle of the bed, turn right to see a sidetable.
Put the lettuce on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Place the heated-up lettuce on the SideTable.

high_descs: however, move the diningtable to the hall.
after reach the hall take the knife in hall table
Take the knife and move to the lettuce in the kitchen.
After reaching the kitchen, open the lettuce rack.
Open the cabinet to take out the knife and use it to slice the vegetable.
then take one slice of lettuce
then move to reach the sink
Take that slice of lettuce and put it in the sink.
Open the water and fill the sink on the sidetable to wash that slice of vegetable.
Take that lettuce slice and move it to the sidetable in the bedroom.
anns.task_desc: Cut the lettuce to move the bedroom SideTable

high_descs: Turn back and walk straight and turn right to reach the dining table
Take a knife from the top of the dining table
Turn left and take few steps and turn right and walk straight to reach the sink
Open the cabinet which is below the sink
Cut the lettuce which is kept inside the cabinet and put the knife in the cabinet
Take the lettuce piece from the cut lettuce and close the cabinet
Head towards the sink
Put the lettuce in the sink, open the faucet, clean the lettuce piece and take off the lettuce piece from the sink
Turn back and walk straight and enter into the bedroom and reach the side table in the room
Put the lettuce piece on the side table
anns.task_desc: Put the lettuce piece on the side table
